issue_statement:
[Env: Functions Support] Consolidate sources endpoint and use v2 only:
Update CLI endpoint for creating sources and always use v2 regardless of sending environment or not:

https://github.com/meroxa/cli/blob/6d8bea31427f5383429a03f1101d1ad48baf228c/cmd/meroxa/root/apps/deploy.go#L63-L64

⚠️ The importance here is to make sure the API path for this endpoint is clearer when no environments is provisioned.

-----

ℹ️  Part of this [EPIC](https://github.com/meroxa/product/issues/665)
pr_title: Always use v2 Source endpoint on App Deploy
pr_description:
## Description of change

We want to consolidate source endpoints and always use v2 on application deploy. 

Fixes [<GitHub Issue>](https://github.com/meroxa/cli/issues/664)
